{"tid":1412961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(廣傳)應對每日記者會嘅對策","createTime":"2019-08-05T08:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T10:34:54.000Z","uid":99374,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e945ffa42c77f571ec8fbf5de8a511b0fdce032d","tid":1412961,"uid":99374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:25:12.000Z","msg":"眾所周知此舉係為咗洗香港人嘅腦<br />\n日日宣傳示威帶嚟嘅暴力<br />\n所以我地除咗要勇武之外 仲要行多一步棋<br />\n<br />\n就係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">由今日開始 堅持推行罷買 <br />\n用購買力向政府示威</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如非有實際必要 例如牙膏M巾<br />\n其他非必要品一律不買<br />\n更唔好同我講 嗰啲咩珍珠奶茶<br />\n或者衫褲鞋襪<br />\n我就唔信你飲少一兩個月你會渴死<br />\n買少幾件衫你要全裸出街<br />\n香港已經處於係危急存亡之際<br />\n仲喺度大吃大喝 得閒出兩個post就當幫左香港<br />\n你嘅良心真係過意得去咩?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁行除咗可以令身陷貿易戰嘅中資公司雪上加霜<br />\n更加可以為將來升級裝備儲彈藥<br />\n當我地捉到政府行得最錯嘅一步棋<br />\n就可以出師有名咁勇武<br />\n<br />\n當然要所有人一齊配合<br />\n不過如果香港人連減少消費都做唔到<br />\n咁光復香港時代革命將只不過係一個口號<br />\n俾你地又要享樂又要拎光環咁去打飛機姐<br />\n<br />\n道理其實人人都明<br />\n只不過如果你願意踏出呢一步<br />\n成為我哋一分子<br />\n咁先有可能真正咁光復香港<br />\n<br />\n香港人 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585b1e8361726dac1d9ccc5fb154bc14ca710f95","tid":1412961,"uid":99374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:30:32.000Z","msg":"有冇人要加入抗爭呀？"},{"pid":"79ca030197d48db34f2837326a15c33610bb5713","tid":1412961,"uid":99374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:30:52.000Z","msg":"定係全部連登仔都淨係識打飛機？"},{"pid":"6e729cc4da55536d8c474c27f240263ccc963df2","tid":1412961,"uid":99374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:31:03.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"be66d9825acda3aa10e47f60a9507e26dc74e560","tid":1412961,"uid":258696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:32:46.000Z","msg":"其實港共都已經好錯<br />\n只係市民思想升lv升得好慢支持減少消費<br />\n希望香港人真係做到"},{"pid":"52dd437427c68dc1046b00c2977de5d2006ec056","tid":1412961,"uid":99374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:37:04.000Z","msg":"Set死線要求回應 -&gt;大遊行<br />\n<br />\n期間儲裝備罷買"},{"pid":"f353bb93b2bf495a6cc712912fef69ba48ea7bcd","tid":1412961,"uid":99374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:37:25.000Z","msg":"冇人記得我地成功方程式？"},{"pid":"9e96ef35d0a5552ad5a1fab6e81f9cf1cdc15039","tid":1412961,"uid":99374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:39:13.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"b46b432b5a193a90ae5193674770fe76aed5a7f9","tid":1412961,"uid":99374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:39:32.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"86d9e44b99be00d6e9e77ead3b4534b8f21d2fdb","tid":1412961,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:42:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcc652b4c83eba9e3828c6661aec36bb65693209","tid":1412961,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:43:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f55a82a9c8ce7045eaf6dcaf1d32d15d35c7f8ff","tid":1412961,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:43:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57adaa71992dbf151e1db55b611e785f45242565","tid":1412961,"uid":99374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:45:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b83452df9537f398127e1b1498280f704adbb349","tid":1412961,"uid":99374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:46:23.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"8f167fe404c560f362c41802fac196d6432ca5dc","tid":1412961,"uid":99374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"9784e9505dc2f62c0258b1fe185ff6f0f3310379","tid":1412961,"uid":99374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:46:43.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"1eabf79d8a59bcf781a50e278853cb0df5035031","tid":1412961,"uid":99374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:46:53.000Z","msg":"4"},{"